EduCertChain/
├── blockchain/
│   └── Blockchain.js              # Custom blockchain implementation
├── server/
│   ├── index.js                   # Express server and API routes
│   └── certRoutes.js              # API handlers for issuing/verifying certs
├── client/
│   ├── index.html                 # Frontend UI
│   ├── style.css                  # UI styling
│   └── script.js                  # Frontend JS (fetch, DOM updates)
├── docker/
│   └── Dockerfile                 # For containerized deployment
├── README.md                      # Documentation
└── package.json                   # Node.js dependencies




Key Features:

Custom blockchain built in JavaScript

SHA256 hashing + Proof of Work

RESTful APIs: Issue & Verify Certificates

Responsive UI for issuing & verifying certs

Chain validity check

Optional Docker deployment
